    <data name="HomePage_Content" xml:space="preserve">
        <value># Welcome to AvaloniaProject!

A modern Avalonia UI desktop application demonstrating MVVM architecture, AOT compilation, and real-time internationalization.

---

## Tech Stack

| Category | Library |
|---|---|
| UI Framework | [Avalonia 12.0](https://avaloniaui.net/) |
| MVVM | [ReactiveUI](https://reactiveui.net/) + Source Generators |
| DI | Splat (constructor injection) |
| Theme | [Semi.Avalonia](https://github.com/irihitech/Semi.Avalonia) + [Ursa](https://github.com/irihitech/Ursa.Avalonia) |
| Icons | [Optris Material Design](https://github.com/Optris/Optris.Icons.Avalonia) |
| Markdown | [LiveMarkdown.Avalonia](https://github.com/giacomelli/LiveMarkdown.Avalonia) |
| Logging | NLog via Splat.NLog |
| Runtime | .NET 10 with AOT |

---

## Architecture Highlights

- **Constructor injection** — all dependencies in composition root (`Program.cs`)
- **AOT-safe ViewLocator** — type dictionary instead of reflection
- **Compiled bindings** — AXAML `x:DataType` with compile-time validation
- **Interface-based** — `ILocalizationService`, `IPageViewModel` for testability
- **Activation lifecycle** — `WhenActivated` / `DisposeWith` for event cleanup
- **Thread-safe localization** — `Lazy&lt;T&gt;` + `INotifyPropertyChanged` for XAML reactivity

---

## Explore

Use the **left sidebar** to navigate between pages:

- **Home** — This page, rendered with LiveMarkdown
- **Binding** — Interactive ReactiveUI binding demonstrations

Use the **title bar** controls to switch languages or toggle the theme.</value>
